from abc import ABC, abstractmethod

class AbstractBase1(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def method_1_p(self):
        pass

class Encapsulated1(AbstractBase1):
    def __init__(self):
        self.__value_1 = 508

    def method_1_p(self):
        return self.__value_1

    def get_value_1(self):
        return self.__value_1

    def set_value_1(self, value):
        self.__value_1 = value

obj1 = Encapsulated1()
obj1.get_value_1()
